name: Tater Tot Breakfast Bake Recipe by Tasty
description: Here's what you need: egg, milk, salt, pepper, breakfast sausage, condensed french onion soup, cheddar cheese, frozen tater tots
recipeIngredient: 2 lb breakfast sausage, crumbled and cooked
recipeInstructionSteps: In a bowl, beat the eggs with milk, salt, and pepper. Set aside.
Spread the sausage over the bottom of a glass 9×13-inch (35 cm x 25 cm) baking dish. Pour on the onion soup, and mix with the sausage.
Sprinkle the cheddar cheese evenly over the top.
Cover with the lined up tater tots, and pour the egg mixture over everything.
Bake uncovered at 350°F (180°C) for one hour.
